#starting
# consider a and b  as place holder 
a = 45
b = 50
# c is to hold the value received for the (+) operation
c = a+b
# print statment for displaying the value inside c variable 
print(c)

# the above operation can be prefomed in the folowing way to

45 + 50
#python will automatically add the two numbers and display the sum '95'
# we do start programming in the above manner to understand some basic fuction and it is a building bass for bigger programming.


